1.title: Site is up to service!!
1.content:
Hello everyone!
My name is Nats and I'm a web developper and am part of a bunch of fandoms. I wanted to create something I could have my own hands on to introduce myself. As such, I decided to put my knowledge of web development to it. I'll try to update it as much as I can so that I won't get rusty （︶^︶）!

I initially thought I could use Carrd to do everything I wanted, but I found it way too restricting and I couldn't put all my creativity at it. So here it is! My own Carrd made by my own hands! I'll try to put more features as time goes on as a side project w/ my studies.

As you probably already seen, I have an old website where I updated all my works I made the past two years, you can find it Here.
You can also find me here :

My art accounts

Hope you will enjoy your stay here!
Until next time!
— Nats
